msgctxt "392_Kiryu"
msgid "Ever heard of 777 Town?"
msgstr "¿Alguna vez has oído hablar de 777 Town?"

msgctxt "404_Shizuka"
msgid "777 Town? What's that?"
msgstr "¿777 Town? ¿Y eso qué es?"

msgctxt "416_Kiryu"
msgid "It's a game for your computer or cell phone. It lets you play pachinko and slots anytime, anywhere you want."
msgstr "Es un juego para el teléfono y la computadora. Te permite jugar al pachinko y a las tragamonedas en cualquier momento y lugar donde sea que estés."

msgctxt "428_Shizuka"
msgid "I see... But I don't really engage in those sorts of activities..."
msgstr "Ya veo... Pero no suelo participar en ese tipo de actividades..."

msgctxt "440_Kiryu"
msgid "All the better then. You can play as much as you want without going to an actual pachinko parlor. Perfect for beginners."
msgstr "Mejor aún. Puedes jugar todo lo que quieras sin tener que ir a un salón de pachinko. Perfecto para principiantes."

msgctxt "452_Shizuka"
msgid "Wow, you're right! I'll try it out the next time I get a chance then."
msgstr "¡Vaya, tienes razón! Entonces lo probaré la próxima vez que tenga la oportunidad."

msgctxt "464_Kiryu"
msgid "Ever heard of Amoebatar?"
msgstr "¿Has oído hablar de Amoebatar?"

msgctxt "476_Shizuka"
msgid "No, I'm afraid not. What is it?"
msgstr "No, me temo que no. ¿Qué es?"

msgctxt "488_Kiryu"
msgid "It's an online community that lets you create an avatar of yourself. The number of members has skyrocketed lately."
msgstr "Es una comunidad en línea que te permite crear un avatar de ti mismo. El número de miembros ha aumentado muchísimo últimamente."

msgctxt "500_Shizuka"
msgid "I've never heard of that! It sounds quite fun."
msgstr "Nunca había oído hablar de eso. Suena muy divertido."

msgctxt "512_Kiryu"
msgid "You can also play games and chat. I'm not much of an expert on those things, so why don't we try it together sometime?"
msgstr "También puedes jugar y chatear. No soy muy experto en esas cosas, así que ¿por qué no lo probamos juntos alguna vez?"

msgctxt "524_Shizuka"
msgid "Yes! Let's try it together!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Probemoslo juntos!"

msgctxt "536_Kiryu"
msgid "Hear about the ghost in the underground mall?"
msgstr "¿Escuchaste sobre el fantasma que hay en el centro comercial subterráneo?"

msgctxt "548_Shizuka"
msgid "Huh!? A ghost!?"
msgstr "¿¡Eh!? ¿¡Un fantasma!?"

msgctxt "560_Kiryu"
msgid "A worker died in an accident during the construction of the underground mall."
msgstr "Un trabajador murió en un accidente durante la construcción del centro comercial subterráneo."

msgctxt "572_Kiryu"
msgid "Now, night after night, his ghost appears to wander the empty mall."
msgstr "Ahora, cuando cae la noche, su fantasma deambula por el centro comercial vacío."

msgctxt "584_Shizuka"
msgid "That must be rather hard for his family. I hope his spirit finds rest someday..."
msgstr "Debe ser muy duro para su familia. Espero que su espíritu encuentre descanso algún día..."

msgctxt "596_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr "Sí..."

msgctxt "608_Kiryu"
msgid "Hear about the footbaths at Yunosono Hot Springs? You don't take off your clothes, so men and women can go in together."
msgstr "¿Has oído hablar de los baños de pies de las Aguas termales Yunosono? No hace falta que te quites la ropa, así que hombres y mujeres pueden entrar juntos."

msgctxt "620_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh, really? Perhaps we could go together sometime."
msgstr "¿En serio? Quizás podríamos ir juntos alguna vez."

msgctxt "632_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure... But you may not have a need to go."
msgstr "Claro... Pero puede que no tengas necesidad de ir."

msgctxt "644_Shizuka"
msgid "Huh? Why do you say that?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Por qué lo dice?"

msgctxt "656_Kiryu"
msgid "Your skin is already so sleek and beautiful. The hot springs might not have any effect."
msgstr "Tu piel ya es tan lisa y hermosa. Puede que las aguas termales no tengan ningún efecto."

msgctxt "668_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh please... You're going to make me blush saying that. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Oh por favor... Va a hacer que me sonroje diciendo eso. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "680_Kiryu"
msgid "Golf is getting pretty popular. A lot of couples go on golf dates lately."
msgstr "El golf se está haciendo muy popular. Últimamente muchas parejas salen a jugar al golf."

msgctxt "692_Shizuka"
msgid "Why yes. When you go around the holes competing for the best score, time just flies because you're having so much fun."
msgstr "Porque sí. Cuando recorres los hoyos compitiendo por la mejor puntuación, el tiempo vuela porque te diviertes mucho."

msgctxt "704_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. We should play sometime."
msgstr "Sí. Deberíamos jugar alguna vez."

msgctxt "716_Shizuka"
msgid "Hehehe. Please go easy on me. ♪"
msgstr "Je, je, je. Por favor sea cuidadoso conmigo. ♪"

msgctxt "728_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you eat liver? Liver contains arachidonic acid, which reverses aging in the brain."
msgstr "¿Has comido higado? El hígado contiene ácido araquidónico, que revierte el envejecimiento del cerebro."

msgctxt "740_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh, really? I never knew that."
msgstr "¿O, de verdad? No lo sabía."

msgctxt "752_Kiryu"
msgid "It also enhances learning. I'm thinking of making my kids back at the orphanage try it."
msgstr "It also enhances learning. I'm thinking of making my kids back at the orphanage try it."

msgctxt "764_Shizuka"
msgid "That's a great idea. I'm sure they'll all turn out very smart."
msgstr "Es una gran idea. Estoy segura de que todos van a salir muy inteligentes."

msgctxt "776_Kiryu"
msgid "Did you know pole dancing is great for working out?"
msgstr "¿Sabías que el pole dance es genial para hacer ejercicio?"

msgctxt "788_Shizuka"
msgid "Pole dancing? You mean that, um... erotic dance?"
msgstr "¿Baile en barra? ¿Te refieres a ese... baile erótico?"

msgctxt "800_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, pole dancers show some skin, but they don't get naked."
msgstr "Well, pole dancers show some skin, but they don't get naked."

msgctxt "812_Kiryu"
msgid "The dance works all your muscles, so it's great for a slim physique."
msgstr "The dance works all your muscles, so it's great for a slim physique."

msgctxt "824_Shizuka"
msgid "I see. I study Japanese dance though, so I don't think I'd have time for something else..."
msgstr "Ya veo. Pero estudio danza japonesa, así que no creo que tenga tiempo para otra cosa..."

msgctxt "836_Kiryu"
msgid "That's right..."
msgstr "That's right..."

msgctxt "848_Kiryu"
msgid "Sweet sake is all the rage now. Women order it all the time when eating at Sushi Gin."
msgstr "El sake dulce ahora está de moda. Las mujeres lo suelen ordenar todo el tiempo en el Sushi Gin."

msgctxt "860_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh, I know! I drink it sometimes myself."
msgstr "¡Oh, lo sé! Yo también lo bebo a veces."

msgctxt "872_Kiryu"
msgid "Sake's traditionally had a dry flavor, but since the sweet varieties have gained popularity, more and more women are starting to drink it."
msgstr "Sake's traditionally had a dry flavor, but since the sweet varieties have gained popularity, more and more women are starting to drink it."

msgctxt "884_Shizuka"
msgid "Yes, it goes well with Japanese food. I could go for some right now, actually."
msgstr "Sí, va bien con la comida japonesa. De hecho, ahora mismo me apetece un poco."

msgctxt "932_Kiryu"
msgid "So about 777 Town..."
msgstr "Acerca del 777 Town..."

msgctxt "944_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh, that pachinko game you told me about the other day, right? I haven't gotten around to it yet, sorry."
msgstr "Oh, ese juego de pachinko del que me hablaste el otro día, ¿verdad? Todavía no lo he probado, lo siento."

msgctxt "956_Kiryu"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

msgctxt "968_Kiryu"
msgid "Have you tried Amoebatar?"
msgstr "¿Has probado Amoebatar?"

msgctxt "980_Shizuka"
msgid "Yes, I did! But it is a bit lonely to play without someone else. It would be great if we could try it out together..."
msgstr "Sí, lo hice. Pero es un poco solitario jugar sin otra persona. Sería genial si pudiéramos probarlo juntos..."

msgctxt "992_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah... Sorry, I know I was the one who asked you to check it out in the first place."
msgstr "Yeah... Sorry, I know I was the one who asked you to check it out in the first place."

msgctxt "1004_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh, no, it's okay. Let's save it for when you have the time."
msgstr "Oh, no, está bien. Dejémoslo para cuando usted tenga tiempo."

msgctxt "1016_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds good."
msgstr "Me parece bien."

msgctxt "1028_Kiryu"
msgid "So about that ghost in the underground mall..."
msgstr "Acerca del fantasma del centro comercial..."

msgctxt "1040_Shizuka"
msgid "I wonder if it's true."
msgstr "Me pregunto si es cierto."

msgctxt "1052_Kiryu"
msgid "Can't say. I sure haven't seen it. It might be just a rumor."
msgstr "Can't say. I sure haven't seen it. It might be just a rumor."

msgctxt "1064_Shizuka"
msgid "I see... Then perhaps no one died in the construction. That's a relief."
msgstr "Ya veo... Entonces tal vez nadie murió en la construcción. Eso es un alivio."

msgctxt "1076_Kiryu"
msgid "Did you try out the footbaths at Yunosono?"
msgstr "¿Probaste los baños de pies en Yunosono?"

msgctxt "1088_Shizuka"
msgid "Wasn't it you who said I don't need to go, sir? ♪"
msgstr "¿No fue usted quien dijo no necesito ir, señor? ♪"

msgctxt "1100_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, true. Sorry, I forgot."
msgstr "Oh, true. Sorry, I forgot."

msgctxt "1112_Shizuka"
msgid "Hehehe. It seems you're tired. Maybe you're the one who needs a little trip to the hot springs."
msgstr "Je, je, je. Parece que está cansado. Tal vez sea usted el que necesite un viajecito a las aguas termales."

msgctxt "1124_Kiryu"
msgid "By the way... Were you one for golf, Shizuka?"
msgstr "Por cierto... ¿Te gustaba el golf, Shizuka?"

msgctxt "1136_Shizuka"
msgid "Not really... I've been playing tennis more as of late."
msgstr "No realmente... Últimamente, he estado jugando más al tenis."

msgctxt "1148_Kiryu"
msgid "Tennis... I see."
msgstr "Tennis... I see."

msgctxt "1160_Shizuka"
msgid "Why don't we play together?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no jugamos juntos?"

msgctxt "1172_Kiryu"
msgid "That sounds nice. Invite me next time when you get the chance."
msgstr "That sounds nice. Invite me next time when you get the chance."

msgctxt "1184_Kiryu"
msgid "Remember that thing liver has that reverses aging in the brain?"
msgstr "Remember that thing liver has that reverses aging in the brain?"

msgctxt "1196_Kiryu"
msgid "What was it called again...?"
msgstr "What was it called again...?"

msgctxt "1208_Shizuka"
msgid "Hehehe. You mean arachidonic acid?"
msgstr "Je, je, je. ¿Se refiere al ácido araquidónico?"

msgctxt "1220_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, that. Wow, you've got a good memory."
msgstr "Yeah, that. Wow, you've got a good memory."

msgctxt "1232_Shizuka"
msgid "You're the one that told me after all. How could I forget? I did a little research on it too!"
msgstr "Al fin y al cabo, fue usted el que me lo había dicho. ¿Cómo podría olvidarlo? ¡También hice una pequeña investigación al respecto!"

msgctxt "1244_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. I see. Seems like you don't need to eat any liver after all."
msgstr "Heh. I see. Seems like you don't need to eat any liver after all."

msgctxt "1256_Kiryu"
msgid "I guess you're not looking into starting pole dancing, right?"
msgstr "I guess you're not looking into starting pole dancing, right?"

msgctxt "1268_Shizuka"
msgid "I'm sorry... I have my traditional Japanese dance."
msgstr "I'm sorry... I have my traditional Japanese dance."

msgctxt "1280_Kiryu"
msgid "I see... That's my bad then."
msgstr "I see... That's my bad then."

msgctxt "1292_Kiryu"
msgid "Have you been drinking sweet sake lately?"
msgstr "Have you been drinking sweet sake lately?"

msgctxt "1304_Shizuka"
msgid "Yes, I have been! But since it's so easy to drink, I'm afraid I had a little too much the other day."
msgstr "Yes, I have been! But since it's so easy to drink, I'm afraid I had a little too much the other day."

msgctxt "1316_Shizuka"
msgid "I think serving drinks to gentlemen like you suits me better."
msgstr "Creo que servirle bebidas a caballeros como usted me sienta mejor."

msgctxt "1328_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, I see..."
msgstr "Je, ya veo..."

